subSection.paragraph:
Post-ocular segment 8 (thorax segment 3; metathorax) about 1.4× longer than preceding segment and about as wide as that as well; rectangular shaped. Ventrally with a pair of prominent appendages (hind leg) [thoracopod 3] (
Figs 2C
; 
3
); basically cylindrical, composed of supposedly five elements; slightly longer than mid leg [thoracopod 2].

